        <title>Alendronate use and bone mineral density gains in women with moderate-severe (stages 3B–5) chronic kidney disease: an open cohort multivariable and propensity score analysis from Funen, Denmark | Archives of Osteoporosis | Springer Nature Link</title>

        
            
    
