    <a data-track="click_references" data-track-action="google scholar reference" data-track-value="google scholar reference" data-track-label="link" data-track-item_id="link" rel="nofollow noopener" aria-label="Google Scholar reference 3" href="http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?&amp;title=Rapid%20cortical%20bone%20loss%20in%20patients%20with%20chronic%20kidney%20disease&amp;journal=J%20Bone%20Miner%20Res&amp;doi=10.1002%2Fjbmr.1916&amp;volume=28&amp;issue=8&amp;pages=1811-1820&amp;publication_year=2013&amp;author=Nickolas%2CTL&amp;author=Stein%2CEM&amp;author=Dworakowski%2CE&amp;author=Nishiyama%2CKK&amp;author=Komandah-Kosseh%2CM&amp;author=Zhang%2CCA&amp;author=McMahon%2CDJ&amp;author=Liu%2CXS&amp;author=Boutroy%2CS&amp;author=Cremers%2CS&amp;author=Shane%2CE">
                    Google Scholar</a> 
                </p></li><li class="c-article-references__item js-c-reading-companion-references-item" data-counter="4."><p class="c-article-references__text" id="ref-CR4">Ensrud KE, Lui LY, Taylor BC, Ishani A, Shlipak MG, Stone KL, Cauley JA, Jamal SA, Antoniucci DM, Cummings SR, Osteoporotic Fractures Research Group (2007) Renal function and risk of hip and vertebral fractures in older women. Arch Gen Intern Med 167(2):133–139</p><p class="c-article-references__links u-hide-print"><a data-track="click_references" rel="nofollow noopener" data-track-label="10.1001/archinte.167.2.133" data-track-item_id="10.1001/archinte.167.2.133" data-track-value="article reference" data-track-action="article reference" href="https://doi.org/10.1001%2Farchinte.167.2.133" aria-label="Article reference 4" data-doi="10.1001/archinte.167.2.133">Article</a> 
